sentence.text: In subgroup analysis, compared with PD patients with initial symptom of tremor and mitochondrial electron transport, ubiquinol to cytochrome c, the positive regulation of glucose transmembrane transport allele frequency of ribosomal large subunit export from nucleus rs34016896 in PD patients with initial symptoms of rigidity/bradykinesia was significantly lower.
